name: Test 1
subject: Intermediate Mathematics
section: Follow the directions. Show all work.

questions.question: Find the greatest common factor of 12 and 18.
Find the least common multiple of 14 and 56.
Colin's grandparents sent him a check for $1,000. He gave $150 to his church, and he spent $396 on school clothes, books, and supplies. How much of the money does he have left?
Jeremy's car can travel 32 miles per gallon of gasoline. How many miles can he travel on 16 gallons of gas?
Megan made 3 1/3 pounds of fudge. She divided it into bags with 2/3 of a pound in each bag. How many bags of fudge did she make?
